WEBVTT

19:14.630 --> 19:16.680 line:80%
so why are you in such a rush to admit it?

19:16.680 --> 19:18.000 line:80%
-You wretched girl...
-Mother!

19:18.000 --> 19:18.590 line:80%
Changyu,

19:19.000 --> 19:20.800 line:80%
I don't care what outsiders think.

19:20.800 --> 19:22.720 line:80%
But the feelings between us
all these years—

19:22.720 --> 19:24.590 line:80%
can they truly be weighed only in
silver and gold?
